{"tid":1011674,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【層次唔同】不屑與余文樂合作 陳冠希開拖鬧陳奕迅楊千嬅：佢哋唔係我朋友","createTime":"2019-02-07T03:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T07:23:21.000Z","uid":147522,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1dbbd25babb81a124be722e935f552da768e1323","tid":1011674,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QfkihbP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQfkihbP.png&h=abebed75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明天才是大年初三，但陳冠希（Edison）提早赤口，日前他在Ig貼旗下品牌CLOT的新tee宣傳，有網民留言希望見到Edison和余文樂旗下品牌MADNESS合作：「Hope to see CLOT X MADNESS next year!」結果觸動了Edison的神經，不但跟網民展開駡戰，更將火頭辣向陳奕迅（Eason）和楊千嬅身上，揚言跟兩人劃清界線，更怒轟Eason和千嬅是蛇蠍小人：「DONT EVEN GET ME STARTED ON THESE SNAKES（唔好將我同啲蛇蠍小人扯上關係）。」<br />\n<br />\nEdison和余文樂N年前因為爭追鍾欣潼，在紅館出席勁歌頒獎禮後台發生撞膊事件，兩男從此種下牙齒印，多年來不相往來，偏偏近年兩人齊齊做埋潮人，分別開設旗下服裝品牌，由娛樂圈鬥到時裝戰場上；日前Edison在社交網晒旗下品牌賀年tee，有網民留言指想看到Edison和樂仔品牌合作，Edison用英文爆粗回應：「Hahaha，你想做甚麼都可以，只是不要在我這裏講廢話，你可以在自己的地方做個廢人，不是在我這裏。」、「我做乜x都可以。」<br />\n<br />\n大批網民加入剝花生，分別留言力撐CLOT和MADNESS，其中有網民留言提到Eason和千嬅：「我對madness無感，但十多年前支持clot而且是你的好朋友@mreasonchan（陳奕迅的IG）和@yeungchinwah（楊千嬅的IG）都轉向支持nadness（編按：madness）了，為甚麼不找找自己的問題呢？」<br />\n<br />\n網民叫Edison自我檢討的言論，成功辣㷫了Edison的神經，他扯火留言：「THEY AINT MY FRIENDS SO THEY CAN DO WHAT THEY WANT &hellip;.. LAMES HANG WITH LAMES &hellip;&hellip; THEY SMALL CITY FOLK &hellip;&hellip; WE ON A DIFFERENT LEVEL &hellip;&hellip;. DONT EVEN GET ME STARTED ON THESE SNAKES.（佢哋唔係我朋友，所以佢想點就點，廢人係同廢人一齊，佢哋係小小嘅都市人，我哋係唔同層次，唔好將我同啲陰險小人扯上關係。）」<br />\n<br />\n豬年伊始，Edison即公開跟昔日好友Eason和千嬅割席，甚至駡兩人是蛇蠍小人，有網民睇唔過眼，留言鬧Edison：「幾衰都好，余文樂比你有家教有口德，成日到處x人哋，黐x線，做人老竇好心你積吓把口啦，唔知自己係度癲咩！」"},{"pid":"96ecf83eea34e627920f92d7e38b2ff52cec5565","tid":1011674,"uid":86628,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T04:40:17.000Z","msg":"做左人老豆仲成個小學雞咁...<br />\nBtw 咁樣唔算爆粗囉"},{"pid":"6608d8cfcae3e64dbaa59fd29909dc8329a6cfec","tid":1011674,"uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T04:41:35.000Z","msg":"連登仔全力支持單春！"},{"pid":"fc17f76639301f34585f94991446231aa43e44f0","tid":1011674,"uid":147047,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T04:50:05.000Z","msg":"Edison 講得岩喎"},{"pid":"8e4450ea0c794885887842dc642453bdaad81159","tid":1011674,"uid":94454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T04:52:15.000Z","msg":"lames hang with lames<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7abf232082abc6d8428fdf104cbb471a166efbf4","tid":1011674,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e4450ea0c794885887842dc642453bdaad81159","tid":1011674,"uid":94454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T04:52:15.000Z","msg":"lames hang with lames<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8d22b442c281d0a5831aafcf1f40f43db7add0","tid":1011674,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:38:34.000Z","msg":"FC鬥FC鬥FC鬥FC鬥"},{"pid":"d36d09cec42099e69ca18d876c64b5efd9684ea1","tid":1011674,"uid":233367,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:40:11.000Z","msg":"都係講事實啫<br />\n<br />\n唔啱聲嘅説話你想唔想聽？"},{"pid":"013cb6528823b32918e55d2bdb4cdcef50d6b41b","tid":1011674,"uid":43557,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:42:18.000Z","msg":"屌原來edison d英文咁撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打到1999"},{"pid":"de30237c02afd1864ad9d7afb49f7f455377611e","tid":1011674,"uid":43730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:05:55.000Z","msg":"淫照單野之後，我反而想知娛樂圈仲有邊個肯同佢做friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgm